<Link id="l00477" /><CodeLine lineNumber="477"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// start(&#95;&#95;llvm&#95;prf&#95;cnts) - start(&#95;&#95;llvm&#95;prf&#95;data)</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00478" /><CodeLine lineNumber="478"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// As we advance to the next record, we maintain the correct CountersDelta</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00479" /><CodeLine lineNumber="479"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// with respect to the next record.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00480" /><CodeLine lineNumber="480"><Highlight kind="normal">      CountersDelta -= </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">sizeof</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal">(&#42;Data);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00481" /><CodeLine lineNumber="481"><Highlight kind="normal">      BitmapDelta -= </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">sizeof</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal">(&#42;Data);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00482" /><CodeLine lineNumber="482"><Highlight kind="normal">    &#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00483" /><CodeLine lineNumber="483"><Highlight kind="normal">    Data++;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00484" /><CodeLine lineNumber="484"><Highlight kind="normal">    ValueDataStart += CurValueDataSize;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00485" /><CodeLine lineNumber="485"><Highlight kind="normal">  &#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00488" /><CodeLine lineNumber="488"><Highlight kind="normal">      <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/amdgpu/silowercontrolflow-cpp/#a4868c5d81c5ccc98c47aeab6244346a0">assert</a>(atEnd());</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00489" /><CodeLine lineNumber="489"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">return</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (</Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">const</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">char</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &#42;)ValueDataStart;</Highlight></CodeLine>
